title: House 4 bedrooms 3.5 bathrooms in Doral
posting_body: ['*BEST RENTAL OPPORTUNITY IN DORAL*', 'Beautiful two-story Single Family home located in the gated community of Madison Pointe.', 'This 4BED/3.5BATH house with high ceilings, impact windows and doors, modern shades, marble floor, open and modern kitchen with quartz countertops, reverse osmosis water filter, SS appliances, double oven, wine cooler, breakfast area, and a family room that provides access to a paved terrace with a gazebo.', 'In the second floor, a master bedroom with a huge walking closet, and master bathroom featuring a roman tub, shower, and two vanities.', 'Two car garage, driveway, water filter and softener throughout the house.', 'Club house with top amenities and great schools all around the area.', 'Fred Ardjmand/ One Stop Realty', 'Licensed Sales Associate', 'Direct:', 'show contact info', 'Coral Gables, Coconut Grove, Pinecrest, Palmetto Bay, Dadeland, Brickell and South Miami rental specialist!', 'Listing Courtesy of Unlimited Real Estate Corp']
